Certainly, the order number is two seven eight nine.

I can arrange that for you. Let me just update our system. Your delivery date is now March fifteenth.

Thank you so much, Roger. I really appreciate your help.

You're welcome, Samantha. Thank you for choosing Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. Have a great day!
